    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new ride that\u2019s ready for all your upcoming adventures? This car has been such a joy to own and it\u2019s still running like a absolute champ! It\u2019s been super well-loved and is looking great inside and out. Whether you're heading out on a weekend road trip or just zipping around town, it's incredibly comfortable and easy to drive. Come on by and take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
