    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the chassis remains communicative and balanced. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its history, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain rigidity remain excellent.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
