      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera offers a visceral driving experience, powered by a 3.6L flat-six engine that breathes through a resonance-tuned intake manifold. The G97 6-speed manual transaxle provides mechanical, short-throw shifts, while the hydraulic steering rack offers the feedback modern EPS systems lack. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the damping rates adjust to road conditions, ensuring the McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension remain settled during high-G maneuvers. Recent service includes a preventive IMS bearing update and a new clutch slave cylinder. The car exhibits excellent mechanical hygiene with a dry crankcase and robust oil pressure. While showing minor cosmetic patina typical of a used performance vehicle, the drivetrain and structural components are in excellent working order.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
